trans-unit.source: Provides a custom CategoryEditor to use for grouping properties that are displayed in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 그룹에 표시 되는 속성에 사용할 사용자 지정 CategoryEditor 제공는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref> class.
Determines which properties are edited by the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 하 여 어떤 속성이 편집 되는지 결정는 <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instance that is checked to determine whether it is included among those properties edited by the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> 가 편집 되는 속성 중 포함 되는지 여부를 확인 하기 위해 검사 되는 인스턴스에 <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this editor edits the specified property; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>이 편집기; 지정된 된 속성을 편집 하는 경우 그렇지 않으면 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref> for the specified <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref> for which to create a new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref>.
Creates a new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref> for the specified <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref> type.
The <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref> type for which to create the new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EditorAttribute"></xref>.

Gets a <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"></xref> that is hosted by the property inspector to provide the user interface for a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.DataTemplate"> </xref> 에 대 한 사용자 인터페이스를 제공 하기 위해 속성 검사자에서 호스팅되는 <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.CategoryEditor"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref:System.Object> that the host can display in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 반환 된 <xref:System.Object>호스트에 표시할 수 있는 한 <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl"> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: The desired [T.Systems.Windows.Size](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) of the image to return.
Gets a localized string that indicates to which category the editor belongs.
trans-unit.target: 편집기 속한 범주를 나타내는 지역화 된 문자열을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Category editors are defined on types and, thus, at load time they need to indicate to which category they belong.
trans-unit.target: 형식에 정의 된 범주 편집기 및 따라서 로드 시 필요한 속한 범주를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that represents the editor category.
